<refsect2>
<title><anchor id="gtk-action-connect-proxy" role="function" condition="since:2.4"/>gtk_action_connect_proxy ()</title>
<indexterm role="2.4"><primary>gtk_action_connect_proxy</primary></indexterm><programlisting><link linkend="void">void</link>                gtk_action_connect_proxy            (<link linkend="GtkAction">GtkAction</link> *action,
                                                         <link linkend="GtkWidget">GtkWidget</link> *proxy);</programlisting>
<para>
Connects a widget to an action object as a proxy.  Synchronises 
various properties of the action with the widget (such as label 
text, icon, tooltip, etc), and attaches a callback so that the 
action gets activated when the proxy widget does.
</para>
<para>
If the widget is already connected to an action, it is disconnected
first.</para>
<para>

</para><variablelist role="params">
<varlistentry><term><parameter>action</parameter>&nbsp;:</term>
<listitem><simpara> the action object
</simpara></listitem></varlistentry>
<varlistentry><term><parameter>proxy</parameter>&nbsp;:</term>
<listitem><simpara> the proxy widget
</simpara></listitem></varlistentry>
</variablelist><para role="since">Since  2.4
</para></refsect2>
